source.name: Wireless Telecommunications Facilities
source.description: Spreadsheets provided by wireless carriers (April 2012) detailing locations of current and proposed telecommunications facilities. Details include location, carrier, type of technology, number of antennas and radio frequency range. A map of these facilities is available in the zip file.  A PDF map can be downloaded from here: http://www.sf-planning.org/ftp/files/publications_reports/library_of_cartography/WirelessMap.pdf
